chunk_title: Check the status of your fine-tuned model
chunk_content: Check the status of your fine-tuned modelAfter you submit your fine-tuning job, you see a page with details about your fine-tuned model. You can find the status and more information about your fine-tuned model on the Fine-tuning > Models page in Azure AI Studio.Your job might be queued behind other jobs on the system. Training your model can take minutes or hours depending on the model and dataset size.
